Hello! Welcome to Harmony Music School. My name is Sean Price. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sean, I am interested in enrolling in some music classes! My name is Kathryn Butler.

Nice to meet you, Kathryn! We're excited to have you join us. To get started, could you please provide your email address?

Sure thing! It's kathryn.b@domain.com.

Thank you, Kathryn. And can I also have your contact number, just in case we need to reach you?

Of course! My contact number is five five five, three two one, seven eight nine zero.

Got it! You seem quite eager, Kathryn. Do you have a particular instrument you're interested in learning?

I'm really excited to start learning the piano!

Wonderful choice! Our piano instructors are amazing. I’ll make sure you get matched with a great teacher.

Thank you for sharing your information, Kathryn. We’ll be in touch soon to finalize your enrollment. Have a fantastic day!
